></a><p id=3D"caption-attachment-150394" class=3D"wp-caption-text">Upgradin=
g Ubuntu to 22.04 LTS using GUI wizard utility</p></div>
Starting in Ubuntu 22.04 LTS, all new versions of Firefox are only availabl=
e via the snap package. So make sure you close all Firefox open tabs and wi=
ndows and let the installer do the transition for you. You may get a system=
 not responding message during such an update. Please do not cancel it and =
click on the wait button. Let the installer do the work:<br>
<div id=3D"attachment_150395" style=3D"width: 609px" class=3D"wp-caption al=
igncenter"><a href=3D"https://www.cyberciti.biz/media/new/faq/2022/04/Upgra=
