grade to the firefox snap" width=3D"599" height=3D"489" class=3D"size-mediu=
m wp-image-150395"></a><p id=3D"caption-attachment-150395" class=3D"wp-capt=
ion-text">Upgrade to the firefox snap</p></div>
You may be prompted to replace or keep a customized config file message. Fo=
r instance (either keep it or replace it as per your needs):<br>
<div id=3D"attachment_150396" style=3D"width: 609px" class=3D"wp-caption al=
igncenter"><a href=3D"https://www.cyberciti.biz/media/new/faq/2022/04/Repla=
