I update file" width=3D"599" height=3D"512" class=3D"size-medium wp-image-1=
50396"></a><p id=3D"caption-attachment-150396" class=3D"wp-caption-text">Re=
place or keep a customized file?</p></div>
We are now reaching the final upgrade stages, and you can either keep or re=
move obsolete packages. I decided to remove them as outdated packages do no=
t receive security updates. But, you may wish to keep them so that system k=
eeps working with older apps. So, be careful with this option (click the De=
tails to see the package list):<br>
<div id=3D"attachment_150397" style=3D"width: 609px" class=3D"wp-caption al=
